{"tid":1718130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"致親愛的中學生們","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T19:04:14.000Z","uid":287112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd41ad04ea4f17dc229a708d6c8e3e08040807c","tid":1718130,"uid":287112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:46:40.000Z","msg":"話說今日路過，見到中學生們放咗學，直接著住學校set rb ，口罩手套都唔戴個，真係嚇到我死。下次可以換件衫先出黎？如果返唔到屋企換，帶定衫換或者著外套拉拉鍊都好呀，如果咁啱有藍屍廢老影到大頭仲要影到校服，比人起底，咁就唔好啦。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，你地見到popo係好好好遠嘅位置清rb ，就大叫叫手足跑，個陣有勁多人係街坊裝同冇gear，只要大家慢慢散開就可以，突然大叫係會嚇親好多手足同街坊架，啲手足又真係跑走，但之後你地知道其實冇事仲跑返返黎添：）所以希望你地唔好一見到popo就跳掣，睇清情況先。如果佢地係跑緊過黎，咁當然係叫人走啦，但如果佢地只係罰企，咁我地都唔洗咁慌張咁跑啦。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，有啲女仔好瘦弱，著住學校體育服加件長袖冷衫但走去扑磚，嚇鬼死我，建議你地幫手落雨開遮會比較好，開遮真係好需要架，特別有好多人遮到上面遮唔到下面，比啲廢老有機可乘影到相。所以唔夠力嘅話，就留返比其他手足做喇。<br />\n<br />\n聽日停課，你地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好</span></span></strong>出街呀，好危險架，教育局都叫大家留係屋企。"},{"pid":"46b2300f66232833b8ba8d295e1c0f4fba93a967","tid":1718130,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:56:01.000Z","msg":"學生哥妹要注意安全<br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>「請廣傳」香港黑警濫權資料庫 (中英日語）</ins></span></strong><br />\n依個網手足籌劃左好一段時間, 包含大量核彈, 請各位出分力廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港警察濫權實錄資料庫<br />\nH.K. Police Violence Database<br />\n香港警察暴行の事件簿</span><br />\n中文<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=efd9ee75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a><br />\nEng<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/en/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fen%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=f5296f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/en/police-timeline/</a><br />\n日文<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/ja/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fja%2Fpolice-timeline&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=87082cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/ja/police-timeline</a>"},{"pid":"ea6c2f5cfe0250209e831ccb337e4ced78d35ee3","tid":1718130,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:02:33.000Z","msg":"願意折壽換所有小朋友平安 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da93d723e252ed06c8a0191942f11e2ec154e33","tid":1718130,"uid":149349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9c4OUpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9c4OUpm.jpg&h=55e8625d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7X1uXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7X1uXH.png&h=673202e9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}